with pytest.raises(TypeError), expected_protocol(ik.toptica.TopMode, [
    "(param-ref 'laser1:serial-number)",
    "(param-set! 'laser1:enable-emission #t)"], [
    "(param-ref 'laser1:serial-number)", 'bloop1',
    "> (param-set! 'laser1:enable-emission #t)", '0', '> '], sep='\n') as tm:
    tm.laser[0].enable = 'True'
